OL,3,CBook published for man who 'inspired
OL,4,Cmillions' during cancer battle
OL,6,FThe book of a Jersey aid worker who
OL,7,Fdied from cancer has been posthumously
OL,8,Freleased.
OL,10,F'A Beginner's Guide to Dying' reflects
OL,11,Fon Simon Boas's life after he received
OL,12,Fa terminal diagnosis.
OL,14,FSimon was diagnosed with advanced
OL,15,Fthroat cancer in 2023, aged 46, and
OL,16,Fpassed away peacefully surrounded by
OL,17,Ffamily on Monday 15 July 2024.
