OL,3,CBook published for man who 'inspired
OL,4,Cmillions' during cancer battle
OL,6,FHis book was published on Thursday 12
OL,7,FSeptember and contains articles from
OL,8,Fthe Jersey Evening Post, as well as
OL,9,FSimon's thoughts on religion, grief,
OL,10,Fand acceptance.
OL,12,FHis candid reflections shared online
OL,13,Fbefore his death were read globally
OL,14,Fwith International Development
OL,15,FMinister Deputy Carolyn Labey
OL,16,Fpreviously describing him as "an
OL,17,Finspiration and larger-than-life
OL,18,Fcharacter who impacted thousands of
OL,19,Flives here in Jersey as well as
OL,20,Fmillions around the world".
