OL,6,FIn the book's foreword, Simon wrote:
OL,7,F"I tried to consider and collate what
OL,8,Fare the things which have given me
OL,9,Fsuch a great sense of peace and
OL,10,Fcontentment and why dying at 46 really
OL,11,Fisn't so bad.
OL,13,F"It's rather short and scrappy (...)
OL,14,Fbut I hope it gives a flavour of how
OL,15,Fit is possible to 'go gentle into that
OL,16,Fgood night', while still living and
OL,17,Floving life to the fullest extent
OL,18,Fpossible."
