OL,6,FSimon first began helping with
OL,7,Fhumanitarian work in 1993 when he
OL,8,Fdelivered his first aid convoy to
OL,9,FBosnia aged 16.
OL,11,FHe spent the last eight years of his
OL,12,Flife in Jersey, working as Jersey
OL,13,FOverseas Aid's Executive Director, and
OL,14,Freceived a rare Silver Seal from
OL,15,FBailiff Sir Timothy Le Cocq for his
OL,16,Fvoluntary work.
