OL,4,Cmillions' during cancer battle
OL,6,FSimon's wife, Aurelie Boas, said on
OL,7,FWednesday's BBC Radio 4 Today
OL,8,Fprogramme that it is a "great
OL,9,Fresponsibility" to be in charge of
OL,10,Fpublishing the book but added it is a
OL,11,F"wonderful" legacy for Simon.
OL,13,FShe explained: "He knew he wouldn't
OL,14,Fsee the book for sure but he saw the
OL,15,Fbook cover made. It was done
OL,16,Fovernight, which I think was a record
OL,17,Ffor the publisher. It was wonderful
OL,18,Ffor him to see the cover.
