OL,6,F"The last few weeks since his death
OL,7,Fhave been very surreal, very amazing
OL,8,Ftoo. I'm very lucky to have great
OL,9,Fsupport and great family."
OL,11,FThe book has already received critical
OL,12,Facclaim with the Daily Mail posing,
OL,13,F"Has anyone ever written a more
OL,14,Finspirational paean to the joy of
OL,15,Flife?"
OL,17,FThe Daily Telegraph concludes, "Boas's
OL,18,Fcheerful stoicism seems to have
OL,19,Ftouched the nation".
